        void handleOption(String key,
                Object value)
                  throws ParseOptionException
        Handles the given option. The key parameter may be an overridable plugin parameter or a supported directive.
        Parameters:
        key - the overridable parameter name or directive name.
        value - the optional value.
        Throws:
        ParseOptionException - if unable to handle the option.
